data.description: Attention Home Buyers! Sellers will help to buy down a lower interest rate for you! That means a lower mortgage payment! That paired with the new lower price, you can walk in with equity! The home is stunning and less than five years old! Not interested in yard work? It's done for you! Schedule to see this luxury end unit townhome today! It's in the coveted Great Bridge Schools area! Two bedrooms with connected bath, large master bed and bath, covered front porch, multiple walk in closets, gourmet, upgraded kitchen with beautiful island and flat top stove; beautiful flooring throughout the home, 9' high ceilings on both floors, garage, driveway and other off-street parking, Granite countertops. Large laundry room. Minutes from the highway and quick access to shopping, restaurants, and other activities. This one is a must see! Schedule your appointment today!
